                                <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td><a href="viewtopic.php?p=77770#77770"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Sat Oct 09, 2004 11:37 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: </span></td>
